EASY,MARKETING,is,an,automated,online,advertising,service,that,has,been,optimized,for,Google,Google,Shopping,Facebook,and,eBay,It,is,designed,to,clearly,and,accurately,show,how,many,new,customers,it,brings,in,the,cost,per,new,customer,acquired,and,the,number,of,new,customers,acquired,over,time,The,EASY,MARKETING,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,information,on,a,shop,s,products,or,product,categories,track,sales,and,leads,create,a,Facebook,like,button,or,push,a,product,to,EASY,MARKETING,for,a,special,promotion,Developers,can,also,embed,ad,campaign,performance,data,analysis,pages,and,quick,charts,on,webpages,using,iFrames,The,website,is,entirely,in,German,but,the,API,documentation,is,in,English